snippet.title: Atari 2600 Game: Star Wars - Return of the Jedi - Ewok Adventure (1983 Parker Bros.) [Prototype]
snippet.description:
A shooting game based on the Star Wars movie Return of the Jedi. You basically control a ship and have limited ammo to fight off opponents. Once you reach your destination, an ally will come and join you in your next fight. The game is restarted from the beginning with increased difficulty. 

Note: The game was never released due to issues with controls.
